      <scopecontent id="aspace_7a0666122e1f3f48a7a58ed53c237200">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Sheridan Papers contain correspondence, manuscripts, speech drafts, printed material and other papers related to the Parliamentary career of Richard Brinsley Sheridan.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
